      <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4">Let's Connect</h1>
        <p class="lead fs-4 mb-0">Have a question or want to discuss a potential project? I'd love to hear from you.</p>
      </div>
